trans-unit.source: Controls the throughput of a service to optimize availability and performance.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollerer enhetstimer for en tjeneste til å optimalisere tilgjengelighet og ytelse.

trans-unit.source: Use the ServiceThrottle to tune the performance characteristics of a service.
trans-unit.target: Bruk av ServiceThrottle til å finstille ytelsen egenskaper for en tjeneste.

trans-unit.source: The easiest way to configure the ServiceThrottle for a service is to use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceThrottlingBehavior>, especially from an application configuration file.
trans-unit.target: Den enkleste måten å konfigurere ServiceThrottle for en tjeneste, er å bruke den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceThrottlingBehavior>, spesielt fra en programmets konfigurasjonsfil.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceThrottlingBehavior>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentCalls%2A> property specifies the maximum number of messages actively processing across all the dispatcher objects in a <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> object.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentCalls%2A>egenskapen angir maksimalt antall meldinger som aktivt behandler på tvers av alle dispatcher-objekter i en <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>objektet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentCalls%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentInstances%2A> property specifies the maximum number of <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> objects in the service.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentInstances%2A>egenskapen angir det maksimale antallet <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekter i tjenesten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentInstances%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentSessions%2A> property specifies the maximum number of sessions a <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> can accept.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentSessions%2A>egenskapen angir maksimalt antall økter en <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>godtar.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ServiceThrottle.MaxConcurrentSessions%2A>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > A trace is written when the first call, <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>, or session is queued on the waitlist.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > En sporing skrives når det første kallet <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>, eller økten er i kø i waitlist.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: The first trace is written as a warning.
trans-unit.target: Første sporingen er skrevet som en advarsel.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the maximum number of messages actively processing across all dispatcher objects in a <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir det maksimale antallet meldinger som aktivt behandler på tvers av alle dispatcher-objekter i en <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The MaxConcurrentCalls property specifies the maximum number of messages actively processing across all the dispatcher objects in a <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> object.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen MaxConcurrentCalls angir det maksimale antallet meldinger som aktivt behandler på tvers av alle dispatcher-objekter i en <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>objektet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: Each channel can have one pending message that does not count against the value of MaxConcurrentCalls until [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] begins to process it.
trans-unit.target: Hver kanal kan ha én ventende meldingen ikke teller mot verdien for MaxConcurrentCalls før [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] begynner å behandle den.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > A trace is written every time the value of this property is exceeded.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > En sporing skrives hver gang verdien for denne egenskapen er overskredet.

trans-unit.source: The upper limit of active messages in the service.
trans-unit.target: Den øvre grensen for aktive meldinger i tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The default is 16 * number of processors in the computer.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er 16 * antall system.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the maximum number of service objects that can execute at one time.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir maksimalt antall serviceobjekter som kan kjøres samtidig.

trans-unit.source: The MaxConcurrentInstances property specifies the maximum number of <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> objects in the service.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen MaxConcurrentInstances angir det maksimale antallet <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekter i tjenesten.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: It is important to keep in mind the relationship between the MaxConcurrentInstances property and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Det er viktig å huske på relasjonen mellom egenskapen MaxConcurrentInstances og <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A> is <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContextMode> the resulting value is the total number of sessions.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A>er <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContextMode>den resulterende verdien er totalt antall økter.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContextMode> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: If <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A> is <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContextMode>, the resulting value is the number of concurrent calls.
trans-unit.target: Hvis <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A>er <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContextMode>, den resulterende verdien er antallet samtidige anrop.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContextMode> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.InstanceContextMode%2A>

trans-unit.source: If a message arrives while the maximum number of <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> objects already exist, the message is held until an <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> object closes.
trans-unit.target: Hvis en melding kommer inn under det maksimale antallet <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekter finnes allerede, meldingen holdes til en <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekt avsluttes.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> </xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > A trace is written every time the value of this property is exceeded.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > En sporing skrives hver gang verdien for denne egenskapen er overskredet.

trans-unit.source: The first trace is written as a warning.
trans-unit.target: Første sporingen er skrevet som en advarsel.

trans-unit.source: The maximum number of <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext> objects in the service at one time.
trans-unit.target: Maksimalt antall <xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>objekter i tjenesten om gangen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.InstanceContext>

trans-unit.source: The default is Maximum Concurrent Calls + Maximum Concurrent Sessions.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er maksimalt antall samtidige anrop + maksimalt samtidige økter.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that specifies the maximum number of sessions a <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost"></xref> object can accept at one time.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir maksimalt antall økter en <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost"> </xref> objektet godtar om gangen.

trans-unit.source: The MaxConcurrentSessions property specifies the maximum number of channels a <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> can accept.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen MaxConcurrentSessions Angir det maksimale antallet kanaler en <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>godtar.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.source: Each listener object can have one pending channel that does not count against the value of MaxConcurrentSessions until [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] accepts the channel and begins processing messages on it.
trans-unit.target: Hvert lytteren-objekt kan ha én ventende kanal ikke teller mot verdien for MaxConcurrentSessions før [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] godtar kanalen og starter behandling meldinger i den.

trans-unit.source: This property is most useful in scenarios that make use of sessions.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er mest nyttig i scenarier som kan bruke økter.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > A trace is written every time the value of this property is exceeded.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > En sporing skrives hver gang verdien for denne egenskapen er overskredet.

trans-unit.source: The first trace is written as a warning.
trans-unit.target: Første sporingen er skrevet som en advarsel.

trans-unit.source: For more information about sessions, see [Using Sessions](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om økter [ved hjelp av økter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Typically, this property is set using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceThrottlingBehavior.MaxConcurrentSessions%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Vanligvis, kan denne egenskapen angis ved hjelp av den <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceThrottlingBehavior.MaxConcurrentSessions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceThrottlingBehavior.MaxConcurrentSessions%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The maximum number of sessions a service host accepts.
trans-unit.target: Maksimalt antall økter tjenestevert godtar.

trans-unit.source: The default is 100 * number of processors in the computer.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er 100 * antall system.
